{"tid":1433491,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE證實「正在拍新歌MV」 Mina人呢？JYP答案讓粉絲怒了","createTime":"2019-08-08T13:30:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T17:04:22.000Z","uid":74065,"like":4,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3af6d1480a02873f13c152725df829547b5cecf8","tid":1433491,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:30:44.000Z","msg":"南韓女團TWICE自出道以來行程滿檔，回歸期也相當密集，日前Mina因身體出現狀況，宣布暫時停止參與活動，8日卻傳出，TWICE正在準備拍攝新歌MV，JYP事後雖證實消息，但關於Mina是否會回歸的回應，卻讓歌迷心疼不已。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4293/d4293636.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4293%2Fd4293636.jpg&h=46c70710&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲TWICE證實正在拍新歌MV。（圖／翻攝自JYP）<br />\n<br />\nTWICE於8日被韓媒爆料正在拍攝新歌MV，而子瑜近來被釋出染成亞麻綠髮色的照片，也極有可能是為了回歸做準備。對此，JYP證實「正在拍攝是事實，但沒辦法公開回歸的日期。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QQ5MiMp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQQ5MiMp.png&h=7912375f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Mina是否會參加MV拍攝，JYP表示「無法確定」，答案令很多粉絲不滿意。（圖／翻攝自TWICE IG）<br />\n<br />\n至於Mina於8月初休養返韓，也被指為是特地回去拍攝MV，但JYP給出的答案卻是「現在無法確認」，讓歌迷更加擔心，在新聞下方留言「希望Mina好好休息不要太急」、「我們願意等」，也有人質疑JYP把行程排得太緊湊，爆氣表示「為何不讓TWICE休息一下」、「不要逼Mina」。<br />\n<br />\nJYP於7月透過官網宣布Mina因患上舞台恐慌症，將不會參加未來所有活動，其中包含正在進行的世界巡迴演唱會，她在1日現身南韓仁川機場時，有些人還以為她已經恢復健康將重新站回舞台上，但她臉色發白、緊抓著媽媽的手，看起來狀況很不好，令歌迷非常擔心。"},{"pid":"b1a43593ecd5a1b07f5d82605012c7bed2089cb1","tid":1433491,"uid":135742,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:31:58.000Z","msg":"第二張相咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89424297313ba40da9efe3e9a0c76a20fdb53d0e","tid":1433491,"uid":238483,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:32:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"def38f21338beb1446330443eda4dff0f3d3f3ab","tid":1433491,"uid":74065,"like":5,"dislike":14,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"b1a43593ecd5a1b07f5d82605012c7bed2089cb1","tid":1433491,"uid":135742,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:31:58.000Z","msg":"第二張相咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:33:09.000Z","msg":"MINA黎"},{"pid":"eb9fba242b3076784601414d18f96bbb2d467a29","tid":1433491,"uid":33359,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:36:45.000Z","msg":"留返多d秒數俾定延"},{"pid":"b5309ff7728c5ab7d71e91fd8524b81ec0c45d15","tid":1433491,"uid":74065,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"eb9fba242b3076784601414d18f96bbb2d467a29","tid":1433491,"uid":33359,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:36:45.000Z","msg":"留返多d秒數俾定延"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:42:17.000Z","msg":"一秒都冇"},{"pid":"4b044ad0fedd7680705aad4f565349d9db2c4a42","tid":1433491,"uid":52073,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5309ff7728c5ab7d71e91fd8524b81ec0c45d15","tid":1433491,"uid":74065,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"eb9fba242b3076784601414d18f96bbb2d467a29","tid":1433491,"uid":33359,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:36:45.000Z","msg":"留返多d秒數俾定延"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:42:17.000Z","msg":"一秒都冇"},"cit